{"id": "test-03380", "text": "NHL ICE HOCKEY - CANUCKS RW BURE SUSPENDED FOR ONE GAME.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 0, "end": 3, "ent_type": "ORG", "text": "NHL"}, {"start": 17, "end": 24, "ent_type": "ORG", "text": "CANUCKS"}, {"start": 28, "end": 32, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "BURE"}]}
{"id": "test-03381", "text": "NEW YORK 1996-12-06", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 0, "end": 8, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "NEW YORK"}]}
{"id": "test-03382", "text": "Vancouver Canucks star right wing Pavel Bure was suspended for one game by the National Hockey League and fined $1,000 Friday for his hit on Buffalo Sabres defenceman Garry Galley on Wednesday.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 0, "end": 17, "ent_type": "ORG", "text": "Vancouver Canucks"}, {"start": 34, "end": 44, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Pavel Bure"}, {"start": 79, "end": 101, "ent_type": "ORG", "text": "National Hockey League"}, {"start": 141, "end": 155, "ent_type": "ORG", "text": "Buffalo Sabres"}, {"start": 167, "end": 179, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Garry Galley"}]}
{"id": "test-03383", "text": "Bure received a double-minor penalty for high-sticking with 2:22 left in the first period of Wednesday's 7-6 overtime win by Vancouver after colliding with Galley in Buffalo zone.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 0, "end": 4, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Bure"}, {"start": 125, "end": 134, "ent_type": "ORG", "text": "Vancouver"}, {"start": 156, "end": 162, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Galley"}, {"start": 166, "end": 173, "ent_type": "ORG", "text": "Buffalo"}]}
{"id": "test-03384", "text": "Galley suffered a concussion and did not return to the game.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 0, "end": 6, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Galley"}]}
{"id": "test-03385", "text": "\"Mr Bure left his feet to deliver a forearm blow to Mr Galley as he was about to be checked legally by his opponent, \"said NHL discipline chief Brian Burke in handing out the suspension.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 4, "end": 8, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Bure"}, {"start": 55, "end": 61, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Galley"}, {"start": 123, "end": 126, "ent_type": "ORG", "text": "NHL"}, {"start": 144, "end": 155, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Brian Burke"}]}
{"id": "test-03386", "text": "\"Although it is clear from the videotape that Mr Bure's actions were a reaction to the impending hit and there was no intent to injure his opponent, there can be no excuse for this type of conduct, \"Burke said.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 49, "end": 53, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Bure"}, {"start": 199, "end": 204, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Burke"}]}
{"id": "test-03387", "text": "Bure, who is struggling with only nine goals and 12 assists in 26 games, will miss Saturday's home game against Ottawa.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 0, "end": 4, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Bure"}, {"start": 112, "end": 118, "ent_type": "ORG", "text": "Ottawa"}]}
{"id": "test-03388", "text": "BOXING - SCHULZ DEFEATS RIBALTA IN IBF HEAVYWEIGHT FIGHT.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 9, "end": 15, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "SCHULZ"}, {"start": 24, "end": 31, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "RIBALTA"}, {"start": 35, "end": 38, "ent_type": "ORG", "text": "IBF"}]}
{"id": "test-03389", "text": "VIENNA 1996-12-07", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 0, "end": 6, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "VIENNA"}]}
{"id": "test-03390", "text": "German Axel Schulz outpointed Cuba's Jose Ribalta in their International Boxing Federation non-title 10-round heavyweight fight on Saturday.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 0, "end": 6, "ent_type": "MISC", "text": "German"}, {"start": 7, "end": 18, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Axel Schulz"}, {"start": 30, "end": 34, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "Cuba"}, {"start": 37, "end": 49, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Jose Ribalta"}, {"start": 59, "end": 90, "ent_type": "ORG", "text": "International Boxing Federation"}]}
{"id": "test-03391", "text": "SOCCER - SPANISH FIRST DIVISION SUMMARY.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 9, "end": 16, "ent_type": "MISC", "text": "SPANISH"}]}
